snippet.title: REIGN OF THE UNDEAD REVOLUTION | CoD4: Custom Zombies - Random Gameplay
snippet.description:
Hey Everyone and Welcome to my first video, where I play some CoD4 Modern Warfare  custom zombies on the FNRP RoTU Revolution Server. It's my personal favorite of all zombie mods for the Call of Duty game series. 

Please Note: There isn't any commentary, but all future videos will have commentary, (unless they don't need it, which won't be often) 

As you can also see, my internet decided to end the video for me, quite useful actually!

Enjoy, Like, Subscribe, Have a Great Day & may God bless it with endless amounts of happiness!

JOIN THE COD4 SERVER: 188.165.234.108:28970
